@startuml CreateAccount
|Admin|
start
:1. Navigate to user management;
:2. Click create new account;
:3. Fill user details (email, role);
:4. Set initial password;
:5. Select role (Student/Teacher/Admin);
:6. Submit;
|AdminPanel|
:7. Validate user data;
|AdminController|
:8. Check email not duplicate;
:9. Create user account;
|Database|
:10. Save user record;
|AdminController|
:11. Send welcome email;
|AdminPanel|
:12. Display confirmation;
:13. Update user list;
stop
@enduml
